    "description": "InfraMantra, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Sales Manager for our Indore operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout InfraMantra:\nInfraMantra is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with InfraMantra!",
